comment.text: This translation key is used to display the title of a directory in various file management contexts. It is likely used in buttons or dialogs that allow users to select a directory from a list, such as a folder selection dialog or a context menu. The value will be displayed next to the folder title, allowing users to easily identify the selected directory.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Armenian translation "WebDAV գրացուցակ" is a literal translation of "directory" but doesn't fully capture the meaning of "WebDAV Directory". It sounds a bit technical and might not be easily understood by all users. A more natural translation might be needed depending on the target audience. "WebDAV թղթապանակ" might be a better option.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider "WebDAV թղթապանակ" or a more context-specific translation for 'WebDAV Directory'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While 'Cartella di WebDAV' is technically correct, a more natural and idiomatic Italian translation for 'WebDAV Directory' would be 'Directory WebDAV' or 'Cartella WebDAV'. The phrase 'Cartella di WebDAV' sounds slightly awkward.

The Lao translation "ໄດເລກະທໍລີ WebDAV" doesn't perfectly capture the meaning of "WebDAV Directory". While 'ໄດເລກະທໍລີ' translates to 'directory', the construction feels slightly unnatural in Lao. A more natural phrasing would emphasize it's a *WebDAV* directory.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ໄດເລກະທໍລີ WebDAV (ໄດເລກະທໍລີ ຂອງ WebDAV)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Romanian translation 'Director WebDAV' is a literal translation but doesn't flow naturally. It would be more idiomatic to use a phrase like 'Dosar WebDAV' or 'Directoriu WebDAV'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Director WebDAV should ideally be 'Director WebDAV' or 'Director WebDAV'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Sinhala translation 'WebDAV නාමාවලිය' is a literal translation of 'directory' (නාමාවලිය) and doesn't fully convey the meaning of 'WebDAV Directory'. It could be misinterpreted.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: WebDAV ෆෝල්ඩර් (WebDAV Folder) or WebDAV répertoire (WebDAV répertoire)
